{"tid":1960292,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急~ FYP問卷 (雨傘運動同反送中運動嘅比較)","createTime":"2020-04-06T05:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T02:32:25.000Z","uid":74948,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"72523718cd77bf23b991f63aeef3b4dda50c37a2","tid":1960292,"uid":74948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"小弟係中大社會科學院嘅學生 (想爆major)，今年做FYP嘅時候唔識死，想做雨革同反送中運動嘅比較研究。<br />\n<br />\n依家仆街啦， 求下咁多位巴打絲打救一救細佬，幫手做份問卷。<br />\n<br />\n問卷link: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/gxL9z2Zz9dBxoeNK9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FgxL9z2Zz9dBxoeNK9&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=ab5ceae5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/gxL9z2Zz9dBxoeNK9</a><br />\n<br />\n問卷裏面有啲字用得比較中性，希望大家明白，社會科學研究要保持中立。<br />\n<br />\n另外有一至兩題嘅選項比較多， 係因為 反送中運動 喺香港 你講真係歷時好長。<br />\n<br />\n裏面嘅選項主要參考 <a href=\"https://www.twreporter.org/a/hong-kong-extradition-law-events，\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twreporter.org%2Fa%2Fhong-kong-extradition-law-events%EF%BC%8C&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=0c645140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.twreporter.org/a/hong-kong-extradition-law-events，</a><br />\n希望大家可以入去重一重溫呢六個月嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n另外，希望大家做完嘅時候可以俾家人做，因為佢研究想收集多啲唔同年齡層/政治取態 (尤其係<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍絲</span>)嘅人嘅意見。<br />\n<br />\n做分我喺做份問卷嘅時候都有 參考呢篇journal article，大家都可以睇睇<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/14742837.2016.1252667?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F14742837.2016.1252667%3F&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=d38461a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/14742837.2016.1252667?</a> journalCode=csms20<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">康復香港，時代抗疫</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔該各位巴打、 絲打!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af7517bb1c7cecfae3785bcdfd1012b9052c186","tid":1960292,"uid":74948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"edbd18fbda07940126f492a040c5f1e5ba748707","tid":1960292,"uid":74948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"推!!!"},{"pid":"33be098714eb0f73abc9b6191c7ac47f80ec2a95","tid":1960292,"uid":74948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:22:01.000Z","msg":"推!!!"},{"pid":"f0f850a8da2eeafbb73de4f9d79505abdab5ff9f","tid":1960292,"uid":119810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:24:54.000Z","msg":"冇規冇矩"},{"pid":"c6a41750bc75b069f5ccffc77f2085211ad3ceb7","tid":1960292,"uid":35857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:27:28.000Z","msg":"冇規冇矩"},{"pid":"1513185e23e9dcba51cd9961b316c0f28708c1ab","tid":1960292,"uid":204227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f5c988bb4e6c9e24fffd065763536bb2cc8c41","tid":1960292,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:36:37.000Z","msg":"btw 幾時開始嗰題冇我個option<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b131dcacd4479583d0f0a84295ee9182169742","tid":1960292,"uid":337616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"好癲 幫幫你手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 蘇蘇嘥銀時同樣被fyp折磨中"},{"pid":"dbce5017a970f20019d1d5cb68d4d48d718dca9d","tid":1960292,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":